SeeD Field Exam - Com Tower Entrance

tip_battle.message: Magic Break, Shell, and Reflect are the perfect abilities to deal with Edea's powerful spells, kupo! Keep an eye on the HP of party members with low Resistance!
tip_battle.title: Edea

sp_scores.title: Exploit Ifrit's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Attack Ifrit with his vulnerability, ice! If you attack him with fire you'll just heal him. Why would you want to do that, kupo?
tip_battle.title: Ifrit

sp_scores.title: Exploit X-ATM092's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: X-ATM092 is vulnerable to lightning, so let the thunder rumble! You'll face it more than once, so keep an eye on your ability uses! Honing your lightning abilities will help keep you from running out!
tip_battle.title: X-ATM092

sp_scores.title: Defeat Biggs and Wedge without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Biggs counter attacks with Lariat when you attack him, so be ready! Once Biggs falls, Wedge joins the battle, so send him packing too, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Biggs & Wedge

sp_scores.title: Exploit BGH251F2's weakness to lightning attacks.

tip_battle.message: When BGH251F2 gets low on HP it uses Beam Cannon, a powerful single-target attack! Blinding it will make the fight much easier, kupo! Then just bring it down fast with lightning, its weakness!
tip_battle.title: BGH251F2

sp_scores.title: Exploit Seifer's weakness to poison attacks.

tip_battle.message: The best way to deal with Seifer's quick attacks is to Slow him down, kupo! Throw in spells like Bio for some poison damage, his personal weakness, and you're sure to win!
tip_battle.title: Seifer
